        <Parent_String>air guns [300203836], projectile launchers with nonexplosive propellant [300222720], projectile weapons with nonexplosive propellant [300208776], projectile weapons [300203727], armaments [300420324], weapons [300036926], Weapons and Ammunition (hierarchy name) [300036743], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
